snippet.title: Pokemon Unbound Mega Evolution + Z-Moves
snippet.description:
A sample of the Mega Evolution, Wish Evolution, Primal Reversion, Ultra Burst, and Z-Move features from Pokemon Unbound. These features are part of a larger battle engine I am working on. As of now, the engine is still undergoing testing and more documentation still needs to be written before it is officially released. The repo for the engine can be found here: https://github.com/Skeli789/Complete-Fire-Red-Upgrade

Credits for the original code of the ability pop-ups and trainer sliding goes to DizzyEgg's Emerald Battle Engine Upgrade V2.0 which can be found here: https://github.com/DizzyEggg/pokeemerald/tree/battle_engine_v2
